# Used by `npx flue dev --target cloudflare` (Worker B local dev). Copy to `.dev.vars`.
# Worker B is a pure model executor; its only runtime concerns are the model specifiers
# (REASONING_MODEL / TUTOR_MODEL in wrangler.jsonc) and provider API keys.
#
# Swapping providers is a one-secret + one-var change here, not a code change — see
# docs/adr/0001-flue-reasoning-worker.md. The tutor-turn stage defaults to TUTOR_MODEL
# (Nemotron via OpenRouter); the other three stages use REASONING_MODEL (OpenAI), so
# Worker B needs BOTH provider keys live.

OPENAI_API_KEY=your-openai-api-key
OPENROUTER_API_KEY=your-openrouter-api-key
